7\u20131945\"]{{Dead link|date=October 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} by John W. Garver\n* [http://www.presbyterian.org.nz/archives/photogallery11/page1.htm Photographs of the war from a Presbyterian mission near Canton]\n* [http://www.microworks.net/pacific/road_to_war/route_south.htm \"The Route South\"]\n\n===Videos===\n* {{YouTube|TRF2WTNwo0M|1937 video-cast of Soong Mai-ling address to the world in English}}\n* {{YouTube|TRF2WTNwo0M|1943 Soong Mai-ling address to the American Congress}}\n* {{YouTube|lQTWtokeF5Q|The Battle of China OWI}}\n* {{YouTube|DcjVWe3xgAo|The Battle of China OWI Pt 2}}\n* {{YouTube|dKTIylgLDHE|The Battle of China OWI Pt 3}}\n* {{YouTube|M6z-fZwpmME|The Battle of China OWI Pt 4}}\n* {{YouTube|VKHk6eepm0E|The Battle of China OWI Pt 5}}\n* {{YouTube|L_zntg-eFF0|The Battle of China OWI Pt 6}}\n* {{YouTube|k0hZiD5Uk5I|The Battle of China OWI Pt 7}}\n\n{{World War II}}\n{{World War II history by nation}}\n{{JapanEmpireNavbox}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Second Sino-Japanese War| ]]\n[[Category:Wars involving Japan]]\n[[Category:Wars involving the Republic of China]]\n[[Category:Anti-Chinese violence in Asia]]\n[[Category:Anti-Japanese sentiment in China]]\n[[Category:China\u2013Japan military relations]]\n[[Category:Invasions by Japan]]\n[[Category:Military history of China during World War II|*]]\n[[Category:Military history of the Republic of China]]\n[[Category:Pacific theatre of World War II]]\n[[Category:Republic of China (1912\u20131949)]]\n[[Category:Religion-based wars]]\n[[Category:Tunnel warfare]]\n[[Category:1930s in China]]\n[[Category:1940s in China]]\n[[Category:Invasions of China]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:1930s in Japan]]\n[[Category:1940s in Vietnam]]\n[[Category:1930s conflicts]]\n[[Category:1940s conflicts]]\n", "name_user": "71.174.99.67", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_Sino-Japanese_War"}
